description:
Generate Dart 3 sealed classes for oneOf with discriminator property.

Tasks (proposal § Task 2.14):
- Generate sealed class as base type
- Generate subclasses with {Base}{Alternative} naming pattern
- Implement factory constructor using discriminator switch
- Handle discriminator property mapping

Spec: openspec/changes/bootstrap-generator/specs/generator-core/spec.md
Design Decision: Decision 6 (Schema Composition - oneOf with discriminator) in openspec/changes/bootstrap-generator/design.md

Example:
sealed class Pet {
  factory Pet.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic> json) {
    switch (json['petType']) {
      case 'cat': return PetCat.fromJson(json);
      case 'dog': return PetDog.fromJson(json);
    }
  }
}

Generate Dart 3 sealed classes for oneOf without discriminator, using try-each deserialization.

Tasks (proposal § Task 2.15):
- Generate sealed class as base type
- Generate subclasses with {Base}{Alternative} naming
- Implement factory constructor that tries each alternative in array order (first to last)
- Return first successful parse

Spec: openspec/changes/bootstrap-generator/specs/generator-core/spec.md
Design Decision: Decision 6 (Schema Composition - oneOf without discriminator) in openspec/changes/bootstrap-generator/design.md

Example:
sealed class Pet {
  factory Pet.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic> json) {
    try { return PetCat.fromJson(json); } catch (_) {}
    try { return PetDog.fromJson(json); } catch (_) {}
    throw FormatException('No match');
  }
}
